py_live14 - https://pickle-reading-bd9.notion.site/py_live-014-a7bc0351f3274040913f97cbb8c4ad0c
py_live15 - https://pickle-reading-bd9.notion.site/py_live-015-170866d71f3e4f9b90ddae001e20c312

- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJOTprYn3e4&t=4740s
- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RotrYLlo3g4

* Criar venv e instalar Django e DRF
- python -m venv venv
- venv/Scripts/activate
- pip install django
- pip install djangorestframework

* Criar e inicializar projeto Django
- django-admin startproject core .
- pip install mysqlclient  (criar squema no mysql)
- python manage.py migrate
- python manage.py createsuperuser

* Rodar o sistema e acessar o admin
- python manage.py runserver

* Filtros RQL em API
- pip install django-rql   (https://django-rql.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting_started/)

* Autenticação por JWT
- pip install djangorestframework-simplejwt


- pip freeze > requirements.txt
